article_title: Benefits of KanCare expansion shared at forum
article_text:
Garden City, KS (67846)

Today

Cloudy early with scattered thunderstorms developing this afternoon. A few storms may be severe. High 74F. Winds W at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 40%..

Tonight

Cloudy skies this evening will become partly cloudy after midnight. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. Low around 50F. Winds NW at 10 to 15 mph.

article_metadata.author: Angie Haflich ahaflich@gctelegram.com

og.description: Expanding Medicaid in Kansas would provide healthcare coverage to more than 150,000 Kansans who currently fall in a coverage gap, help struggling rural hospitals keep their doors open, and inject
